            <note xml:id="foot.f2">CD cited Turner, on the authority of Kölliker and Langer, on this point in <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1966.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Descent</hi></ref> 1: 209.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">See <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_4436.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Kölliker 1855</ref>, pp. 558–61.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f4">See <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_4572.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Langer 1852</ref>.</note>
